{%- comment -%}
  Shipping and Returns
  Uses isyf-legal-* classes from isyf-base.css (shared text styles)
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="isyf-legal-page">
  <div class="isyf-legal-content">
    <h1 class="isyf-legal-title">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Shipping</h2>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><strong>Europe</strong><br>
    Delivery: 5-10 business days<br>
    Free shipping on orders over 100 EUR<br>
    Standard shipping: 5.99 EUR</p>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><strong>North America</strong><br>
    Delivery: 7-14 business days<br>
    Free shipping on orders over 150 EUR<br>
    Standard shipping: 12.99 EUR</p>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><strong>Rest of World</strong><br>
    Delivery: 10-20 business days<br>
    Shipping calculated at checkout</p>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph"><strong>Print-on-demand items</strong><br>
    Please allow an additional 2-5 business days for production before shipping.</p>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Returns</h2>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">We offer a <strong>30-day return policy</strong> from the date of delivery.</p>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">To be eligible for a return:</p>
    <ul class="isyf-legal-list">
      <li>Item must be unworn, unwashed, and in original condition</li>
      <li>Original tags must be attached</li>
      <li>Item must be in its original packaging</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">To initiate a return, email us at <strong>contact@iseeyoufeel.com</strong> with your order number.</p>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Refunds</h2>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">Once we receive and inspect your return, refunds are processed within <strong>5-7 business days</strong>. The refund will be credited to your original payment method. Please note that your bank may take additional time to process the credit.</p>

    <h2 class="isyf-legal-section-title">Exchanges</h2>

    <p class="isyf-legal-paragraph">We do not offer direct exchanges. If you need a different size or color, please return the original item and place a new order.</p>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping and returns",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
